dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents addresses for Buffalo County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Buffalo_Addresses_2018.gdb.[Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[Site Address Points]
